## Manual Testing SHAP

```bash
# Test dengan data kecil (< 10 samples)
curl -X POST https://mwd-backend-production-f958.up.railway.app/api/v1/shap/explain \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"model":"porosity","data":[{"DEPTH":2000,"Gamma Ray - Corrected gAPI":50,"Resistivity Phase - Corrected - 2MHz ohm.m":100,"Corrected Drilling Exponent unitless":1.5,"ROP for the Bit - Distance Over Time (On Bottom) m/s":0.1,"Surface Torque Average N.m":5000,"Weight On Bit N":10000,"Chrom 1 Total Gas Euc":5}],"top_n":3}'
```

**Catatan**: Prediksi ini akan butuh 1-2 menit.